{"tid":2103415,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"韓國電影屍殺半島最新預告片(已經證實咗有香港)","createTime":"2020-07-11T07:35:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-13T11:30:15.000Z","uid":267658,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"381e5b3270ad3789b065182bc71a329c765f7eed","tid":2103415,"uid":267658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T07:35:12.000Z","msg":"故事簡介<br />\n香港史上NO.1賣座亞洲電影《屍殺列車》暑假飆速殺入香港！上集列車駛往釜山後，喪屍病毒瞬間全國爆發，4年後的韓國屍毒遍野，被全球孤立，淪為死城。所餘無幾的生還者踏上最後一艘難民船，離開被世人遺棄的朝鮮半島。退伍軍人正錫(姜棟元 飾)和家人有幸登上難民船，但一上船便發現喪屍潛伏，幸得香港收容，這批韓國人才得以上岸，以「半島難民」身分在香港重新生活。但正錫受不住金錢誘惑，加入了一個回國竊取巨額美金的行動。他和隊友重返韓國，竟然發現仍有一班未受屍毒感染的人在掙扎求存，正錫決定帶這班倖存者逃生，他們最後能否成功逃出屍殺半島？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ya3w5GbWgmk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fya3w5GbWgmk&d=FEUhZFrEoh9TukhHyG%2BZyK6fvQnHzZYMiebojCBKDlo%3D&h=4d0b67d4\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ya3w5GbWgmk</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nxFDIAk1zGk&amp;t=21s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DnxFDIAk1zGk%26t%3D21s&d=FEUhZFrEoh9TukhHyG%2BZyK6fvQnHzZYMiebojCBKDlo%3D&h=a7449e81\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nxFDIAk1zGk&amp;t=21s</a>"},{"pid":"f6f3dabc8a5d52366eb582934aa02df5ecd79df1","tid":2103415,"uid":4917,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T07:43:03.000Z","msg":"見到個鬥獸場覺得爛"},{"pid":"ae638d05fcb859cad3e0f2cb4795d2926d2636ae","tid":2103415,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T11:30:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />韓仔片"}]}